Package com.smartsheet.api.internal.http

Class HttpEntitySnapshot

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.smartsheet.api.internal.http.HttpEntity
      • com.smartsheet.api.internal.http.HttpEntitySnapshot
  • public class HttpEntitySnapshot
extends HttpEntity
    this extension of HttpEntity is only for the purpose of creating a copy of its data stream so that the original can be used as-received and this duplicate can be logged if needed

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      HttpEntitySnapshot​(HttpEntity original)
      this ctor creates a snapshot of the original entity (which requires its stream either support reset or it must be entirely consumed and replaced with an exact copy)
